ZH: 今年冬天寒流来得特别早。
EN: The cold wave came unusually early this winter.

ZH: 寒流使得城市的气温骤降到零下十度。
EN: The cold wave caused the temperature in the city to plummet to minus ten degrees.

ZH: 夏天我们都期待能够逃离这里的寒流。
EN: We all look forward to escaping the cold wave here in the summer.

ZH: 这个寒流导致了很多道路结冰，交通出现了严重问题。
EN: This cold wave has caused many roads to freeze, resulting in severe transportation issues.

ZH: 我们需要做好应对寒流的准备，保持足够的防寒措施。
EN: We need to be prepared to tackle the cold wave and take necessary measures to keep warm.

ZH: 这次寒流可能导致农作物受损。
EN: This cold wave may cause damage to crops.

ZH: 整个国家都感受到了来自北方的强烈寒流。
EN: The entire country has felt the impact of the strong cold wave from the north.

ZH: 这个城市的居民冬天经历了严寒的寒流。
EN: The residents of this city experience the bitter cold of the cold wave in winter.

ZH: 预计寒流将持续一周左右的时间。
EN: It is expected that the cold wave will last for about a week.

ZH: 寒流来袭，人们都纷纷穿上了厚厚的羽绒服。
EN: As the cold wave approaches, people have started wearing thick down jackets.

ZH: 寒流的影响使得海洋中的温度骤降。
EN: The impact of the cold wave caused a sudden drop in the temperature of the ocean.

ZH: 这次寒流可能会给野生动植物带来危险。
EN: This cold wave may pose a threat to wildlife.

ZH: 这个地区的居民都在忍受着严寒的寒流。
EN: The residents of this region are enduring the severe cold of the cold wave.

ZH: 大风加上寒流，使得天气更加寒冷。
EN: The combination of strong winds and the cold wave makes the weather even colder.

ZH: 在这个季节，寒流会给人们的生活带来很多不便。
EN: During this season, the cold wave brings a lot of inconvenience to people's lives.

ZH: 现在正是寒流肆虐的季节。
EN: It is now the season when the cold wave is raging.

ZH: 这个地区的居民都在期待寒流的终结。
EN: The residents of this area are all looking forward to the end of the cold wave.

ZH: 人们纷纷买入厚实的被子以备寒流的来袭。
EN: People are buying thick comforters in preparation for the cold wave.

ZH: 我们需要保护好自己，以应对寒流给我们带来的不便。
EN: We need to take care of ourselves to cope with the inconvenience caused by the cold wave.

ZH: 去年的寒流给这个地区的农业带来了严重的灾害。
EN: Last year's cold wave caused severe agricultural disasters in this region.
